{"tid":953782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"祝施永青聖誕快樂，有一個開心嘅平安夜","createTime":"2018-12-24T07:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T05:39:23.000Z","uid":20058,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"36a19b0f176e5ab4efe55c4649459e8d96382351","tid":953782,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d2f385159ab9a9c99ac12b29b3ef610b1645da","tid":953782,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"大家快啲嚟祝佢聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455b17f35bf411eb34968432bbd99449c900c65d","tid":953782,"uid":138409,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T07:45:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20121218/51189997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20121218%2F51189997&d=s%2BPAoeUTXyRCnWzRG5Mam0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=a2e52a4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20121218%2F51189997&h=f1ad1725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20121218/51189997</a><br />\n<br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有HardFeeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"62c68cc0662300aef5d9a56515458bac0020301f","tid":953782,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14958366bd0e72c877a16dfdb50d7fc6c0b5619","tid":953782,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656d8e36188fcb23c3db953f62eaf7c3650530d7","tid":953782,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceaef9205432baa4b60ed541e5906a3a2678687","tid":953782,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8977be5d4d07c8ccf96eafe9eed5bd48db9539e6","tid":953782,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa